                     <interp inst="t18280221-76-person602" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw the prisoner in Hawker's custody, and found the pot of paste about twenty yards down Windsor-street; I cannot say the prisoner dropped it; it was not between the shop, and where he was taken.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280221-76-person603">
